categories: Category:Cut content from Star Wars: The Old Republic

nodes.text: The venom cattail was a plant that grew on the planet Quesh.

The venom cattail was originally supposed to be introduced in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, in the companion conversations with the Jedi Knight companion Doc. However, the mission where the player would accompany Doc to Quesh and retrieve the cattail was cut before the game's release.
